get_angl_direction(int *is_r_down, int *is_r_left, double ang)

is_r_down | is_r_left
_____________________
0         | 0       | right top / south & east
0         | 1       | left top / south & west
1         | 0       | right down / north & east
1         | 1       | left down / north & west
_____________________